<P>
ENGLAND -- CULTURE; TELEVISION INDUSTRY -- ENGLAND; LEGISLATION -- ENGLAND; 
TELEVISION PROGRAMMING; BROADCAST RIGHTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
