ANDREW; MURDER IN MISSISSIPPI (MOTION PICTURE); SOUTHERN UNITED STATES -- 
HISTORY; BLACKS -- HISTORY; MURDERS -- MISSISSIPPI; CIVIL RIGHTS MOVEMENT 
