sea view is worth and how government can ensure that a room with a view stays 
that way. Linda Castile, above, and her husband, Brett, are asking the Del Mar 
City Council to help them retrieve their ocean view at their home, where their 
vista is now blocked by condominium construction. BOB GRIESER / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
