</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Kathryn McCamant and Charles Durrett, co-authors of "CoHousing: a Contemporary 
Approach to Housing Ourselves," will address a meeting Feb. 23, at 8 p.m., at 
the Bayview Plaza Holiday Inn in Santa Monica. 
</P>
<P>
