New York's Metropolitan Museum of Art on ancient Toltec sacrifices into 
practice. 
</P>
<P>
THE DRAWING OF THE THREE by Stephen King (Signet: $5.95). Hours after 
overcoming the opposition of a powerful sorcerer, Roland is thrust into another 
challenge, and the 20th Century. 
</P>
