SELF-HELP / REFERENCE 
</P>
<P>
YOUR BEST IS GOOD ENOUGH: Aging Parents and Your Emotions by Vivian E. 
Greenberg (Lexington: $16.95). Clinical advice for adults who serve as care 
givers to their immediate families and who find themselves stretched to the 
limit when their parents require some of the same supports. 
</P>
<P>
THE SCHOOLS SEARCH GUIDE TO PRIVATE SCHOOLS FOR STUDENTS WITH LEARNING 
DISABILITIES by Midge Lipkin Ph.D. (Schoolsearch: $29.95; (617) 489-5785). 
Directory of 300 schools in the United States, including information on costs, 
faculty evaluations, tests and requirements, and an approach to learning 
disabilities. 
</P>
