</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
ALLA BREVE: ARIAS, DUETS AND OVERTURES BY VERDI, DONIZETTI, ROSSINI, GOUNOD, 
MOZART AND LEHAR. KATHLEEN BATTLE, SOPRANO; PLACIDO DOMINGO, TENOR; 
METROPOLITAN OPERA ORCHESTRA CONDUCTED BY JAMES LEVINE. DEUTSCHE GRAMMOPHON 427 
686-2 (COMPACT DISC). 
</P>
