<HEADLINE>
<P>
TWO LEADING LADIES OF THE SCREEN LEAVE BEHIND SWEET MEMORIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Barbara Stanwyck always said of herself that she was lucky and that she merely 
"did her job." Luck turned out to be sheer talent, and her "job" sheer 
artistry. 
</P>
<P>
She was an actress who never gave less than everything. 
</P>
<P>
GREGORY FARMER 
</P>
<P>
Brea 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
