Age: 41 
</P>
<P>
Occupation: City councilman, real estate sales 
</P>
<P>
Background: Owner of a land-banking firm that buys real estate and sells to 
builders. City Council member for one year. 
</P>
<P>
Issues: Ethics in government, transportation. 
</P>
<P>
Contributions: $273,500 (includes $270,000 loan to himself). 
</P>
