</P>
<P>
Background: Secretary of Orange County Democratic Central Committee. 
Co-chairwoman of state Democratic Party's Affirmative Action Committee. Former 
high school teacher and former owner of a North Carolina bed-and- breakfast 
inn. Democratic nominee in 1988 for this seat. Ran for New York Assembly in 
1982. 
</P>
<P>
Issues: Pro-choice on abortion. Long-term health care, prenatal care. 
</P>
