for Assembly 5n Orange County as Republican in 1966. Joined Democrats in 1970. 
Founder in 1965 of Partners for Progress, an organization to create jobs for 
minorities. 
</P>
<P>
Issues: Children, as they are affected by drugs, gang violence and education. 
</P>
<P>
Contributions: Less than $1,000. 
</P>
