County in 1978. Switched parties in 1988. Leader in a committee called Throw 
the Rascals Out. 
</P>
<P>
Issues: Ethics in government. Wants to limit the terms of elected officials. 
</P>
<P>
Contributions: $1,260 (includes $925 loan to himself) 
</P>
